--------------------------------------------------
ATURAN WAJIB - JANGAN LUPA KILL SANDBOX
--------------------------------------------------

Setiap kali pakai E2B, WAJIB kill sandbox setelah selesai.
Kalau lupa, sandbox terus jalan dan billing sampai timeout 1 jam.

Contoh benar di app/api/agent/optimize/route.ts:

  const sandbox = await Sandbox.create({
    apiKey: process.env.E2B_API_KEY,
  })

  try {
    const execution = await sandbox.runCode(code)
    const result = JSON.parse(execution.text || '{}')
    return result
  } finally {
    await sandbox.kill()  // <-- WAJIB ada di finally block
  }

Pakai try/finally agar sandbox PASTI terkill
meskipun ada error di tengah eksekusi.

